                <img class="ui medium rounded right floated image" src="/img/ww.jpg" alt="Whitewater Image">
                <p>
                    The majority of our members that join the club are mostly focused on whitewater. The skills we teach
                    you on day one will be of use to you in all disciplines of kayaking, but more often than not we are
                    preparing you for river trips. From fresher trips at Clashganny to traveling abroad, whitewater
