            <div class="ui sixteen wide column">
                <h1 class="ui dividing header">Polo</h1>
                <img class="ui medium rounded right floated image" src="/img/polo.jpg" alt="Polo Image">
                <p>
                    The Club will usually play polo in the pool once a week and will hold outdoor training days on the
                    lead up to competitions such as ICUP. What is Polo? Polo is a team of players where they throw the
                    ball between them, aiming to score goals by throwing the ball into a 2m x 1m rectangular goal
                    suspended 2m above water level. While in possession teams will pass the ball around and try to
                    create enough space near the opposition goal to take a shot. The defending team will set up a 'zone'
                    around their own goal which they will try to keep all of the attackers out of. All of this involves
                    a lot of crashing into each other, pushing boats around and you are allowed to capsize people by
                    pushing them on the shoulder when they have the ball!
                </p>
            </div>

